{"type":null,"faqId":48029,"title":"帐户设置","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{font-weight:bold;}\n.s2{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.41527778in;}\n.p1{text-indent:1.0979167in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:0.5104167in;margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{text-indent:1.0208334in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{text-indent:-0.110416666in;margin-left:1.18125in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p5{margin-left:1.0708333in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p6{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p7{margin-left:1.15625in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">切换邮件帐户</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>XE \"切换邮件帐户\"XE \"更改邮箱帐户\"</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>如果手机上登录了多个邮件帐户，在浏览或发送邮件前，请先切换到要使用的邮件帐户。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s2\">1.  </span><span>打开“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177892\" style=\"width:0.25555557in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”“电子邮件”。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s2\">2.  </span><span>在“收件箱”界面，点击屏幕左上角的</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177893\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>，打开帐户列表。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s2\">3.  </span><span>点击要使用的邮件帐户。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span class=\"s1\">删除邮件帐户</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p6\">\n<span>XE \"删除邮件帐户\"XE \"删除帐户\"</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span>1.打开“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177894\" style=\"width:0.25555557in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”“电子邮件”。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span>2.在“收件箱”界面，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177895\" style=\"width:0.22916667in;height:0.16319445in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span> &gt; 设置”。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span>3.选择要删除的邮件帐户。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span>4.点击“删除帐户”,然后点击“确定”。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p6\">\n<span>删除邮件帐户后，手机将停止收发该邮箱的邮件。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p6\">\n<span class=\"s1\">个性化邮件帐户</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p6\">\n<span>设置显示发件人头像、删除邮件后显示的画面，以及更改签名、设置收件箱同步频率、更改邮件通知铃声等，打造您个性化的帐户。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p6\">\n<span>XE \"个性化邮件帐户\"XE \"更改邮件帐户设置\"XE \"设置签名\"XE \"设置收件箱\"</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span>1.打开“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177896\" style=\"width:0.25555557in;height:0.18680556in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”“电子邮件”。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span>2.在“收件箱”界面，点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=177897\" style=\"width:0.22916667in;height:0.16319445in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span> &gt; 设置”，根据需要完成设置。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p7\"></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":136,"faqType":"信息与邮件","useful":7,"unUseful":4,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"3615","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-SMS-Email","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1445598094000,"seriesProductName":"RIO-AL00,RIO-CL00,RIO-TL00,RIO-UL00,RIO-UL10","visitedTimes":80,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}